Abilities.As a Chosen:
{{Main|Chosen of Mystra}}
Being a Chosen of Mystra, Alustriel was well-regarded as a highly-capable and naturally-talented spellcaster, She was also exempt from a variety of spells, giving her immunity to being [[polymorph other|''polymorphed'' by another]], ''[[feeblemind]]ed'', or having her [[flesh to stone|flesh turned to stone]], as well as being ''[[chill touch]]ed'', ''[[web]]bed'',  ''[[sink|sunk]]'', or targeted by either a ''[[forcecage]]'' or a ''[[lightning bolt]]'', all rounded off by ''[[time stop]]''.

Conversely, Lady Silverhand had a selection of spells that she was able to cast at will, once every day. She could ''[[comprehend languages]]'', ''[[detect thoughts]]'', ''[[polymorph any object]]'', ''[[shapechange]]'', and ''[[teleport without error]]''. Alustriel was also capable of using ''[[clairaudience/clairvoyance|clairaudience]]'' and ''[[minor creation]]'', ''[[hold monster|holding monster]]s'', or causing an ''[[anti-magic shell]]''.
